# UI APIs

Does not require authentication.

## Get Applications

Returns all available applications (grouped).

```APIs
GET https://dev.zoomsymbols.com/api/ui/getApplications
```

> Parameters (OPTIONAL)

```
isMobile: true/false
```

> Response

```json
{
  "result": [{
      "application_group_id": "1",
      "application_group_code": "markets",
      "application_group_name": "Markets",
      "application_id": 1,
      "application_name": "markets_overview",
      "application_title": "Markets Overview",
      "can_repeat": true,
      "short_description": null,
      "application_type_id": null,
      "application_type_code": null,
      "application_type_name": null,
      "list_order": 1,
      "is_favorite": false,
      "user_can_access": false
      },
  ...
  ]
}
```

