## Save Dashboard Item

Save an item from the dashboard.

```APIs
POST https://dev.zoomsymbols.com/api/ui/dashboards/save
```

> Parameters

```
id: item_id
title: item_title
applications: [array of apps] (each app represnted by its data stored in an object)
list_order: item_list_order
is_selected: true/false (false by default)
view_mode: item_view_mode ('tabs' by default)
```

> Response

```json
{
  "result": "Updated"
}
```
